======================================================================

  H → (α₁,α₂) at n=7: 52/72 values of H are ambiguous

  Examples of H with multiple (α₁,α₂) decompositions:
    H= 15: [(3, 2), (7, 0)]
    H= 17: [(6, 1), (8, 0)]
